{"version": "1.0", "gameId": "qi-qin-meng-huo", "description": "《七擒孟获》对话数据 - 第1关完整对话集", "dialogs": [{"id": "l1_opening_zhuge_01", "levelId": "level_01", "trigger": "level_start", "speaker": "诸葛亮", "speakerTitle": "汉·丞相", "portrait": "zhuge_liang_normal", "text": "将士们，此战所求，非杀戮，乃归心。孟获虽悍，然南中之地，不可力取，只可攻心。", "skippable": true, "firstPlayLockSec": 2.0, "nextDialog": null, "audioCue": "dialog_zhuge"}, {"id": "l1_opening_zhuge_02", "levelId": "level_01", "trigger": "after_l1_opening_zhuge_01", "speaker": "诸葛亮", "speakerTitle": "汉·丞相", "portrait": "zhuge_liang_normal", "text": "西洱河畔，乃南蛮门户。此战若胜，七擒之计，方有开局。随我前进。", "skippable": true, "firstPlayLockSec": 1.5, "nextDialog": null, "audioCue": "dialog_zhuge"}, {"id": "l1_player_thought_01", "levelId": "level_01", "trigger": "after_opening", "speaker": "玩家", "speakerTitle": "士卒视角", "portrait": "player_default", "text": "(攻心...？丞相的意思是，我们打赢了还不能杀敌？)", "skippable": true, "firstPlayLockSec": 1.0, "nextDialog": null, "audioCue": null, "isInnerMonologue": true}, {"id": "l1_old_soldier_tip_01", "levelId": "level_01", "trigger": "enter_combat_area", "speaker": "老兵张伯", "speakerTitle": "汉军老兵", "portrait": "zhang_bo_tip", "text": "新来的？小心点，蛮子们的骨头比石头还硬。别硬冲，找空档再射！", "skippable": true, "firstPlayLockSec": 0, "nextDialog": null, "audioCue": "dialog_veteran", "displayType": "bubble_fade"}, {"id": "l1_old_soldier_tip_02", "levelId": "level_01", "trigger": "player_hp_low_first_time", "speaker": "老兵张伯", "speakerTitle": "汉军老兵", "portrait": "zhang_bo_worried", "text": "受了伤就后撤！活着才能打仗，别逞能！", "skippable": true, "firstPlayLockSec": 0, "nextDialog": null, "audioCue": "dialog_veteran", "displayType": "bubble_fade"}, {"id": "l1_boss_intro_menghuo_01", "levelId": "level_01", "trigger": "boss_arena_enter", "speaker": "孟获", "speakerTitle": "南蛮大王", "portrait": "menghuo_arrogant", "text": "哈哈哈！汉人竟敢踏入我南中之地！来者何人？报上名来，本大王象蹄之下，不死无名之辈！", "skippable": false, "firstPlayLockSec": 3.0, "nextDialog": null, "audioCue": "dialog_boss", "cameraEffect": "zoom_in_boss"}, {"id": "l1_boss_intro_menghuo_02", "levelId": "level_01", "trigger": "after_l1_boss_intro_menghuo_01", "speaker": "孟获", "speakerTitle": "南蛮大王", "portrait": "menghuo_arrogant", "text": "我的战象踏平过无数军队！你们这些瘦弱的汉兵，还不够它塞牙缝的！", "skippable": false, "firstPlayLockSec": 2.0, "nextDialog": null, "audioCue": "dialog_boss"}, {"id": "l1_boss_phase2_taunt", "levelId": "level_01", "trigger": "boss_hp_50_percent", "speaker": "孟获", "speakerTitle": "南蛮大王", "portrait": "menghuo_angry", "text": "哼！有点门道...但还不够！看我的！", "skippable": false, "firstPlayLockSec": 1.5, "nextDialog": null, "audioCue": "dialog_boss_enraged"}, {"id": "l1_capture_menghuo_01", "levelId": "level_01", "trigger": "boss_defeated", "speaker": "孟获", "speakerTitle": "南蛮大王", "portrait": "menghuo_defeated", "text": "诡计！汉人狡诈，我不服！若堂堂正正一战，胜负未可知！放我下来！", "skippable": false, "firstPlayLockSec": 3.0, "nextDialog": null, "audioCue": "dialog_capture", "sceneEffect": "capture_animation"}, {"id": "l1_capture_menghuo_02", "levelId": "level_01", "trigger": "after_l1_capture_menghuo_01", "speaker": "孟获", "speakerTitle": "南蛮大王", "portrait": "menghuo_defeated_angry", "text": "此次输在地利不熟，非你等武力胜我！放我回去，整顿兵马，再来决战！", "skippable": false, "firstPlayLockSec": 2.5, "nextDialog": null, "audioCue": "dialog_capture"}, {"id": "l1_release_zhuge_01", "levelId": "level_01", "trigger": "cutscene_release_start", "speaker": "诸葛亮", "speakerTitle": "汉·丞相", "portrait": "zhuge_liang_calm", "text": "孟获将军，今日擒你，非为羞辱。南中之地，需你我共治，而非征战不休。", "skippable": false, "firstPlayLockSec": 3.0, "nextDialog": null, "audioCue": "dialog_zhuge_release", "bgmChange": "bgm_cutscene_calm"}, {"id": "l1_release_zhuge_02", "levelId": "level_01", "trigger": "after_l1_release_zhuge_01", "speaker": "诸葛亮", "speakerTitle": "汉·丞相", "portrait": "zhuge_liang_calm", "text": "（转向士卒们）放他走吧。今日放他，是为了明日不再有战。这便是——攻心为上。", "skippable": false, "firstPlayLockSec": 3.0, "nextDialog": null, "audioCue": "dialog_zhuge_release"}, {"id": "l1_release_menghuo_reaction", "levelId": "level_01", "trigger": "after_l1_release_zhuge_02", "speaker": "孟获", "speakerTitle": "南蛮大王", "portrait": "menghuo_confused", "text": "...你...你什么意思？打赢了不放我走？诸葛亮，你在打什么算盘？", "skippable": false, "firstPlayLockSec": 2.5, "nextDialog": null, "audioCue": "dialog_boss_confused"}, {"id": "l1_player_thought_02", "levelId": "level_01", "trigger": "after_release_scene", "speaker": "玩家", "speakerTitle": "士卒视角", "portrait": "player_confused", "text": "(...为什么打赢了还要放他走？丞相到底在想什么？)", "skippable": true, "firstPlayLockSec": 2.0, "nextDialog": null, "audioCue": null, "isInnerMonologue": true}, {"id": "l1_result_victory_01", "levelId": "level_01", "trigger": "level_complete", "speaker": "系统", "speakerTitle": "", "portrait": null, "text": "第一擒 · 西洱河初战 — 完成", "skippable": true, "firstPlayLockSec": 0, "nextDialog": null, "audioCue": "victory_fanfare", "displayType": "result_banner"}], "strategyAdviceTemplates": {"aggressive": "你锐气可嘉，然南中地势诡谲。下关切记：勇不可无，躁不可有。", "steady": "你能稳步推进，已得用兵之要。前路更险，仍须先观其势，再发其箭。", "struggling": "胜败乃兵家常事。南中之险，不在一敌一阵，而在不熟其地。慢行，细看。", "explorer": "你善察细节，此为良习。战场之中，往往一处火把、一段足迹，便是破局之机。"}}